edBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:39:27.000Z","msg":"呂麗搖巴肯覆我未？咩plan都冇就洗bot叫人入去機場送頭好不負責任。<br />\n你一日唔講922點入機場、有咩plan我都會問落去。<br />\n3條link咩內容都冇，吹1點嘅雞但叫人1230睇連登/Tg等消息係咩玩法<br />\n比你地班機場Admin撚足3次，唔想再有人被撚<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n不服來辨<br />\n宜家搞機場和理塞係冇意義<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574643\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574643</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57bba86330a956b54746a9636c6828639570d4e6","tid":1574892,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"唔可以玩得太多<br />\n記住係市面上一樣好多真假藝員<br />\n當然呢點都係目標既一部份<br />\n連自己都迷惑埋一份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10698d886e348d6edb95dbce3b109e4543dfbd2a","tid":1574892,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"超.暗黑兵法<br />\n<br />\n急不及待"},{"pid":"9ab21f6de474af61d5a4283620946d28a91d46fd","tid":1574892,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31ab3d1a4b05e3015c37a8b963032de8a9fcca44","tid":1574892,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:42:16.000Z","msg":"依個係幾搞鬼"},{"pid":"a360187a612e44ab72d0be5064f73c0ab4f0360b","tid":1574892,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"如果手足扮狗 俾人告冒警事少<br />\n 分分鐘俾我哋自己友當係真臥狗 全民打狗wo<br />\n呢個位要諗諗點解決"},{"pid":"bbc772e136a5c96ab632066d47f4b5b3ce913691","tid":1574892,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a360187a612e44ab72d0be5064f73c0ab4f0360b","tid":1574892,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"如果手足扮狗 俾人告冒警事少<br />\n 分分鐘俾我哋自己友當係真臥狗 全民打狗wo<br />\n呢個位要諗諗點解決"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"其實真係好迷<br />\n唯有唔好自己一個出去開show<br />\n帶多兩個朋友仔 <br />\n幫手去自己人個邊打下眼色講解下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果想拎棒棒既就自己小心啦<br />\n但係上面個d對白同行動呢 唔洗表明自己係狗<br />\n反正4點鐘都叫左大家拭目以待<br />\n作為一個痴線藝術家 太投入追求都係一種罪惡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e72992c389255fce63ec017ba4c0ebd33b171e9","tid":1574892,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"偷偷地推多野就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c0d38965912bad1c1c4297e62cb33c74e5f07c","tid":1574892,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"忍唔住又黎多野"},{"pid":"3f308123b471c668f7c025a110da9169c03c3758","tid":1574892,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52041689e5ba685d2beb615bd31b47e12a54b748","tid":1574892,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"咁我自己又推下"},{"pid":"3d2e15c121c68ecc3eb1aabea4c3c7e0e946260a","tid":1574892,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbc772e136a5c96ab632066d47f4b5b3ce913691","tid":1574892,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a360187a612e44ab72d0be5064f73c0ab4f0360b","tid":1574892,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"如果手足扮狗 俾人告冒警事少<br />\n 分分鐘俾我哋自己友當係真臥狗 全民打狗wo<br />\n呢個位要諗諗點解決"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"其實真係好迷<br />\n唯有唔好自己一個出去開show<br />\n帶多兩個朋友仔 <br />\n幫手去自己人個邊打下眼色講解下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外如果想拎棒棒既就自己小心啦<br />\n但係上面個d對白同行動呢 唔洗表明自己係狗<br />\n反正4點鐘都叫左大家拭目以待<br />\n作為一個痴線藝術家 太投入追求都係一種罪惡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"一句講晒<br />\n救人打狗"}]}